 * Snow Tech grinned at Dracona, then followed his
sister down the hallway. After a couple of steps,
Shadow Cat is interupted from her latest hunt (namely,
Dinobot) By Ramulus, who told them they could come to
fight with him. The only thing that Shadow Cat liked
more than cute bots with even cutter tails(or other)
was battle. She grinned at him,*

 " Sure, sounds like fun, lets go!"

 * And with that she followed Ramulus out of the base.
Snow Tech yelled after her,"*

 " I'm stayin here, If Inny wakes up i want to suprise
the slag out of her!" 

 * And with an evil chuckle, he walked towards Irons
spark signature.*

 *meanwhile Shadow Cat had run off with Ramulus,
looking forward to battle, when her com-system beeped,
loudly. She stopped, confused. She pushed the little
button, annoyed that her fun was being interupted. A
hologram of their small ship appeared. It's sheild
defences where failing, and it didn't have any other
defences, being a small ship. So, with a sigh, she
walked towards it, hopping that the sheilds didn't
fail, and the predacons didn't get a hold of their
cargo.....*

 * Snow Tech's com-system beeped, just as he was
raising his fist to knock on iron's door, why did all
his fun have to be interupted all the time? frowning,
he pushed it. The hologram appeared, showing the ships
distress. He sighed, he had to go, their cargo was too
valuble to let anyone get a hold of. Snow Tech smiled,
the ships deffences might fall, and the Preds might
get in, but HIS deffence system was still there. Let
the Predacons TRY to get to the hold, the only way
they'de get there is in tiny bits.....*
